Choose Your Champion is back! Sixteen players are heading to Taipei for the HCT World Championship—pick your champion and earn card packs if they advance through the competition!

You’ll receive one Rastakhan’s Rumble card pack just for participating! You’ll receive an additional card pack each time your champion advances to the quarterfinals, semifinals, or finals. If your champion plays in the finals, for example, you would earn six total packs (including your participation pack). All card packs will be delivered to you in-game the week after the World Championship.

Voting ends on April 25 at 3:30 CEST. Remember to choose carefully, because you can't change your champion once you've locked in your selection.

